{
  "stem": "19518.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, the laws, our anti-Semitic laws, like [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a priest who was a senator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pristerova. ?] They instilled in the '30s that there will be no kosher handling of the animals to slaughter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They installed the anti-Jewish money laws, which were introduced to the Polish public.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nothing to compare with what was with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That really did not compare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We still were allowed to live like people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we still were allowed to keep our-- whatever we owned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We still were allowed to, to have that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, as I was growing up, these things weren't as good as we thought it might be, but we lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I recall, and I don't remember exactly if it was just before the war in '39 or a year prior to that, when the slaughterhouse were closed for Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Jews went out on strike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you know, in our history, we have these three weeks between one fast and Tisha B'av.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We did not, by any means, we did not buy any chickens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Jews in Cracow did not eat meat, strictly dairy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the, the Polish-- that was must have been a year prior to the outbreak of the war, because the Polish population themselves objected to that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because the farmers were bringing chickens and what to the market, and they had no-- there was no, there were no sales.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they did not like that idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And somehow it was re-voted for a, for a, for a little while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was not as good as it used to be, like my mom used to tell me years ago.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe I did not remember as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism was in Poland, rampant.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
